      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="In the Indirect Tax Reporting and Compliance process,  indirect tax(IDT) reports are generated from SAP S/4 HANA. After the report is reviewed and reconciliated, the IDT form is prepared for tax filling, posting to target sales &amp; use tax or VAT account, and process tax payment. By introducing the SAP DRC functionality, most of the manual processes could be automated."/>
